Package de.interactive_instruments.model.std

Standard domain model items

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Id
    An universal interface for identifying domain model items.
    IdFactory
    A factory interface for constructing Id objects.
    IdMap<V>
    An interface that simplifies the mapping of Id objects to values.
    RetrievableItem
    A domain model item that possesses an Id and a label.
    RetrievableItemMap<T extends RetrievableItem>
    An interface that simplifies the mapping of RetrievableItem objects to values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultId
    The default identifier implementation for domain model items.
    DefaultIdFactory
    The default Id factory implementation for constructing DefaultId objects.
    DefaultIdMap<V>
    An object that simplifies the mapping of Id objects to values.
    DefaultRetrievableItemMap<T extends RetrievableItem>
    An object that simplifies the mapping of RetrievableItem objects to values.
    IdMap.StrEqContainer  
    ManagedItemRegistry<T extends RetrievableItem & Releasable>
    An abstract class for managing objects that implement the RetrievableItem and the Releasable interface.
